    "36651801": {
      "title": "Complete genome sequence of Bartonella ancashensis strain 20.00, isolated from the blood of a patient with verruga peruana",
      "abstract": "ABSTRACT Here we present the complete genome sequence of Bartonella ancashensis strain 20.00, isolated from the blood of a Peruvian patient with verruga peruana, known as Carrion9s disease. Bartonella ancashensis is a Gram-negative bacillus, phylogenetically most similar to Bartonella bacilliformis, the causative agent of Oroya fever and verruga peruana."
